title: Houdini 4 Pro UCI Chess Engines [v1x, preactivated]
description:
=====================================================
 Houdini 4 Pro UCI Chess Engines [v1x, preactivated]
===================================================== 

This package includes the preactivated 32-bit engine and both 64-bit engines (A and B). No serial nor registry entries needed. 

A UCI-compatible GUI such as Arena, Fritz, Shredder, etc is required (not included). This v1 version also works in Aquarium. Please refer to cruxis-dot-com for complete details. 

UCI = Universal Chess Interface
GUI = Graphical User Interface

All credit the immortals... CG101, CBF, x, and friends!
